Problem Statement

Predict the percentage of a student based on the number of study hours. What will be the 
predict score if a student studies for 9.25 hrs/day?



solution

simple Linear Regression is performed with the train-test-split technique for machine learning 
implementation.The visualization part of the Data to use Scatter plot to identify the ralationship 
between two variables and also after preprocessing regression line is plotted.At end of the model 
error is calculeted then the model is give r^2 is better.
